{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Last year when I was here, I was speaking to you about a swim"},{"time":3000,"text":"which I did across the North Pole."},{"time":6000,"text":"And while that swim took place three years ago,"},{"time":8000,"text":"I can remember it as if it was yesterday."},{"time":11000,"text":"I remember standing on the edge of the ice,"},{"time":14000,"text":"about to dive into the water,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and thinking to myself, I have never ever"},{"time":19000,"text":"seen any place on this earth"},{"time":21000,"text":"which is just so frightening."},{"time":23000,"text":"The water is completely black."},{"time":25000,"text":"The water is minus 1.7 degrees centigrade,"},{"time":28000,"text":"or 29 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"time":31000,"text":"It's flipping freezing in that water."},{"time":34000,"text":"And then a thought came across my mind:"},{"time":37000,"text":"if things go pear-shaped on this swim,"},{"time":40000,"text":"how long will it take for my frozen body"},{"time":43000,"text":"to sink the four and a half kilometers"},{"time":45000,"text":"to the bottom of the ocean?"},{"time":47000,"text":"And then I said to myself, I've just got to get this thought"},{"time":49000,"text":"out of my mind as quickly as possible."},{"time":51000,"text":"And the only way I can dive"},{"time":53000,"text":"into that freezing cold water"},{"time":55000,"text":"and swim a kilometer"},{"time":57000,"text":"is by listening to my iPod and really revving myself up,"},{"time":60000,"text":"listening to everything from beautiful opera"},{"time":63000,"text":"all the way across to Puff Daddy,"},{"time":66000,"text":"and then committing myself a hundred percent --"},{"time":68000,"text":"there is nothing more powerful than the made-up mind --"},{"time":71000,"text":"and then walking up to the edge of the ice"},{"time":74000,"text":"and just diving into the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"And that swim took me"},{"time":78000,"text":"18 minutes and 50 seconds,"},{"time":80000,"text":"and it felt like 18 days."},{"time":82000,"text":"And I remember getting out of the water"},{"time":84000,"text":"and my hands feeling so painful"},{"time":86000,"text":"and looking down at my fingers,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and my fingers were literally the size of sausages"},{"time":91000,"text":"because -- you know, we're made partially of water --"},{"time":94000,"text":"when water freezes it expands,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and so the cells in my fingers"},{"time":98000,"text":"had frozen and expanded"},{"time":100000,"text":"and burst."},{"time":102000,"text":"And the most immediate thought when I came out of that water"},{"time":104000,"text":"was the following:"},{"time":106000,"text":"I'm never, ever"},{"time":108000,"text":"going to do another cold water swim"},{"time":111000,"text":"in my life again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"Anyway, last year, I heard about the Himalayas"},{"time":117000,"text":"and the melting of the -- (Laughter)"},{"time":119000,"text":"and the melting of the glaciers"},{"time":121000,"text":"because of climate change."},{"time":123000,"text":"I heard about this lake, Lake Imja."},{"time":126000,"text":"This lake has been formed in the last couple of years"},{"time":129000,"text":"because of the melting of the glacier."},{"time":131000,"text":"The glacier's gone all the way up the mountain"},{"time":133000,"text":"and left in its place this big lake."},{"time":136000,"text":"And I firmly believe"},{"time":138000,"text":"that what we're seeing in the Himalayas"},{"time":140000,"text":"is the next great, big battleground"},{"time":142000,"text":"on this earth."},{"time":144000,"text":"Nearly two billion people --"},{"time":146000,"text":"so one in three people on this earth --"},{"time":148000,"text":"rely on the water from the Himalayas."},{"time":151000,"text":"And with a population increasing as quickly as it is,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and with the water supply from these glaciers --"},{"time":156000,"text":"because of climate change --"},{"time":158000,"text":"decreasing so much,"},{"time":160000,"text":"I think we have a real risk of instability."},{"time":162000,"text":"North, you've got China; south, you've India, Pakistan, Bangladesh,"},{"time":165000,"text":"all these countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"And so I decided"},{"time":169000,"text":"to walk up to Mt. Everest,"},{"time":171000,"text":"the highest mountain on this earth,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and go and do a symbolic swim"},{"time":175000,"text":"underneath the summit"},{"time":177000,"text":"of Mt. Everest."},{"time":179000,"text":"Now, I don't know if any of you have had the opportunity to go to Mt. Everest,"},{"time":182000,"text":"but it's quite an ordeal getting up there."},{"time":185000,"text":"28 great, big, powerful yaks"},{"time":187000,"text":"carrying all the equipment up onto this mountain --"},{"time":190000,"text":"I don't just have my Speedo,"},{"time":192000,"text":"but there's a big film crew who then"},{"time":194000,"text":"send all the images around the world."},{"time":197000,"text":"The other thing which was so challenging about this swim"},{"time":200000,"text":"is not just the altitude."},{"time":202000,"text":"I wanted to do the swim at 5,300 meters above sea level."},{"time":205000,"text":"So it's right up in the heavens."},{"time":207000,"text":"It's very, very difficult to breath. You get altitude sickness."},{"time":210000,"text":"I feels like you've got a man standing behind you with a hammer"},{"time":213000,"text":"just hitting your head all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"That's not the worst part of it."},{"time":217000,"text":"The worst part was this year was the year where they decided"},{"time":219000,"text":"to do a big cleanup operation on Mt. Everest."},{"time":222000,"text":"Many, many people have died on Mt. Everest,"},{"time":225000,"text":"and this was the year they decided to go"},{"time":227000,"text":"and recover all the bodies of the mountaineers"},{"time":229000,"text":"and then bring them down the mountain."},{"time":232000,"text":"And when you're walking up the mountain"},{"time":234000,"text":"to attempt to do something"},{"time":236000,"text":"which no human has ever done before, and, in fact, no fish --"},{"time":239000,"text":"there are no fish up there swimming at 5,300 meters --"},{"time":242000,"text":"When you're trying to do that,"},{"time":244000,"text":"and then the bodies are coming past you,"},{"time":246000,"text":"it humbles you,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and you also realize very, very clearly"},{"time":250000,"text":"that nature is so much more powerful"},{"time":253000,"text":"than we are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"And we walked up this pathway,"},{"time":257000,"text":"all the way up."},{"time":259000,"text":"And to the right hand side of us"},{"time":261000,"text":"was this great Khumbu Glacier."},{"time":263000,"text":"And all the way along the glacier we saw"},{"time":265000,"text":"these big pools of melting ice."},{"time":268000,"text":"And then we got up to this small lake"},{"time":271000,"text":"underneath the summit of Mt. Everest,"},{"time":273000,"text":"and I prepared myself"},{"time":275000,"text":"the same way as I've always prepared myself,"},{"time":277000,"text":"for this swim which was going to be so very difficult."},{"time":279000,"text":"I put on my iPod, I listened to some music,"},{"time":282000,"text":"I got myself as aggressive as possible --"},{"time":284000,"text":"but controlled aggression --"},{"time":286000,"text":"and then I hurled myself"},{"time":288000,"text":"into that water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"I swam as quickly as I could"},{"time":293000,"text":"for the first hundred meters,"},{"time":295000,"text":"and then I realized very, very quickly,"},{"time":297000,"text":"I had a huge problem on my hands."},{"time":299000,"text":"I could barely breathe."},{"time":301000,"text":"I was gasping for air."},{"time":303000,"text":"I then began to choke,"},{"time":305000,"text":"and then it quickly led to me vomiting in the water."},{"time":308000,"text":"And it all happened so quickly:"},{"time":311000,"text":"I then -- I don't know how it happened -- but I went underwater."},{"time":314000,"text":"And luckily, the water was quite shallow,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and I was able to push myself off the bottom of the lake"},{"time":320000,"text":"and get up and then take another gasp of air."},{"time":323000,"text":"And then I said, carry on. Carry on. Carry on."},{"time":325000,"text":"I carried on for another five or six strokes,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and then I had nothing in my body,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and I went down to the bottom of the lake."},{"time":333000,"text":"And I don't where I got it from,"},{"time":335000,"text":"but I was able to somehow"},{"time":337000,"text":"pull myself up and as quickly as possible"},{"time":340000,"text":"get to the side of the lake."},{"time":343000,"text":"I've heard it said that drowning"},{"time":345000,"text":"is the most peaceful death that you can have."},{"time":348000,"text":"I have never, ever heard"},{"time":350000,"text":"such utter bollocks."},{"time":352000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":354000,"text":"It is the most frightening and panicky feeling"},{"time":357000,"text":"that you can have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"I got myself to the side of the lake."},{"time":361000,"text":"My crew grabbed me,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and then we walked as quickly as we could"},{"time":365000,"text":"down -- over the rubble --"},{"time":367000,"text":"down to our camp."},{"time":369000,"text":"And there, we sat down,"},{"time":371000,"text":"and we did a debrief about what had gone wrong"},{"time":374000,"text":"there on Mt. Everest."},{"time":376000,"text":"And my team just gave it to me straight."},{"time":379000,"text":"They said, Lewis, you need to have"},{"time":381000,"text":"a radical tactical shift"},{"time":384000,"text":"if you want to do this swim."},{"time":386000,"text":"Every single thing which you have learned"},{"time":388000,"text":"in the past 23 years of swimming,"},{"time":390000,"text":"you must forget."},{"time":392000,"text":"Every single thing which you learned"},{"time":394000,"text":"when you were serving in the British army,"},{"time":396000,"text":"about speed and aggression,"},{"time":398000,"text":"you put that to one side."},{"time":400000,"text":"We want you to walk up the hill in another two days' time."},{"time":403000,"text":"Take some time to rest and think about things."},{"time":406000,"text":"We want you to walk up the mountain in two days' time,"},{"time":409000,"text":"and instead of swimming fast,"},{"time":412000,"text":"swim as slowly as possible."},{"time":414000,"text":"Instead of swimming crawl, swim breaststroke."},{"time":417000,"text":"And remember, never ever swim with aggression."},{"time":420000,"text":"This is the time to swim"},{"time":422000,"text":"with real humility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424000,"text":"And so we walked back up"},{"time":426000,"text":"to the mountain two days later."},{"time":428000,"text":"And I stood there"},{"time":430000,"text":"on the edge of the lake,"},{"time":432000,"text":"and I looked up at Mt. Everest --"},{"time":434000,"text":"and she is one of the most beautiful mountains on the earth --"},{"time":437000,"text":"and I said to myself, just do this slowly."},{"time":440000,"text":"And I swam across the lake."},{"time":442000,"text":"And I can't begin to tell you"},{"time":444000,"text":"how good I felt"},{"time":446000,"text":"when I came to the other side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"But I learned two very, very"},{"time":450000,"text":"important lessons there on Mt. Everest,"},{"time":453000,"text":"and I thank my team of Sherpas who taught me this."},{"time":456000,"text":"The first one is"},{"time":458000,"text":"that just because something has worked in the past so well,"},{"time":461000,"text":"doesn't mean it's going to work in the future."},{"time":464000,"text":"And similarly,"},{"time":466000,"text":"now, before I do anything,"},{"time":468000,"text":"I ask myself what type of mindset"},{"time":470000,"text":"do I require"},{"time":472000,"text":"to successfully complete a task."},{"time":475000,"text":"And taking that into the world of climate change --"},{"time":478000,"text":"which is, frankly,"},{"time":480000,"text":"the Mt. Everest of all problems --"},{"time":482000,"text":"just because we've lived the way we have lived for so long,"},{"time":485000,"text":"just because we have consumed the way we have for so long"},{"time":488000,"text":"and populated the earth the way we have for so long,"},{"time":491000,"text":"doesn't mean that we can carry on"},{"time":493000,"text":"the way we are carrying on."},{"time":495000,"text":"The warning signs are all there."},{"time":498000,"text":"When I was born, the world's population"},{"time":500000,"text":"was 3.5 billion people."},{"time":502000,"text":"We're now 6.8 billion people,"},{"time":505000,"text":"and we're expected to be 9 billion people"},{"time":507000,"text":"by 2050."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"And then the second lesson,"},{"time":511000,"text":"the radical, tactical shift."},{"time":513000,"text":"And I've come here to ask you today:"},{"time":516000,"text":"what radical tactical shift"},{"time":519000,"text":"can you take in your relationship to the environment,"},{"time":522000,"text":"which will ensure"},{"time":524000,"text":"that our children and our grandchildren"},{"time":526000,"text":"live in a safe world"},{"time":528000,"text":"and a secure world,"},{"time":530000,"text":"and most importantly, in a sustainable world?"},{"time":533000,"text":"And I ask you, please, to go away from here"},{"time":535000,"text":"and think about that one"},{"time":537000,"text":"radical tactical shift"},{"time":539000,"text":"which you could make,"},{"time":541000,"text":"which will make that big difference,"},{"time":543000,"text":"and then commit a hundred percent to doing it."},{"time":546000,"text":"Blog about it, tweet about it, talk about it,"},{"time":549000,"text":"and commit a hundred percent,"},{"time":551000,"text":"because very, very few things"},{"time":553000,"text":"are impossible to achieve"},{"time":555000,"text":"if we really put our whole minds to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"So thank you very, very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}